Flowers for International Women’s Day are nice, but they won’t close the gender pay gap. At Applifting, we make sure that women earn the same as their male colleagues with the same work experience. 👩‍🚀🧑‍🚀How can we be so sure? With our open salaries based on proven skills, we simply know how much every one of us makes. 💸

How does it all work?
Every Applifter has a competency model for their role that describes the knowledge and skills they should possess at any given level. So we know exactly what to improve on, and it’s up to us how fast we grow—regardless of our gender and identity. Our professional and financial growth is entirely in our hands. 🚀

While we did give our female colleagues small gifts on this special day, we believe that constant development and equal opportunities throughout the year are more valuable than one small gift and recognition on one dedicated day. 🤔 We believe in creating a culture of trust and transparency, where everyone is valued and compensated fairly.
